 《愚弄我一次》在哪里拍摄？ 《Peaky Blinders》拍摄地点已确定https://www.nme.com/news/tv/where-is-fool-me-once-filmed-peaky-blinders-location-3565744?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=where-is-fool-me-once- 《巅峰黑帮》拍摄地点Adam StarkeyThu, 04 Jan 2024 20:40:58 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3565744 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="骗我一次" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>两部剧共用一个特定的拍摄地点</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/where-is-fool-me-once-filmed-peaky-blinders-location-3565744">《愚弄我一次》在哪里拍摄的？ 《Peaky Blinders》的拍摄地点已确认，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="骗我一次" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>与作家哈兰·科本 (Harlan Coben) 最新合作的《愚弄我一次》( <em>Fool Me Once)</em>已成为又一热门作品。</p><p>这部由八部分组成的惊悚剧改编自同名小说，讲述了前士兵玛雅（米歇尔·基冈饰）的故事，她在家中放置的秘密保姆摄像头上发现了被谋杀的丈夫乔（理查德·阿米蒂奇饰）。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/fool-me-once-ending-explained-what-happened-in-the-new-netflix-hit-series-3564692">“愚弄我一次”结局解释：Netflix 新热门剧集中发生了什么？</a></strong></li></ul><p>剧情简介如下：“当前士兵玛雅在秘密保姆摄像头中看到她被谋杀的丈夫时，她发现了一个追溯到过去的致命阴谋。”</p><p>除基冈和阿米蒂奇外，该剧的演员阵容还包括阿迪尔·阿赫塔尔、乔安娜·林利、埃米特·J·斯坎兰和迪诺·费彻。</p><h2> <em>《愚弄我一次》</em>在哪里拍摄？ </h2><figure id="attachment_3565752" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3565752" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3565752" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3.jpg" alt="骗我一次" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Fool-Me-Once-main-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3565752" class="wp-caption-text"> 《骗我一次》。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>虽然原著以纽约为背景，但该剧将整个故事转移到了英国——特别是英格兰西北部。</p><p>该剧以虚构的温赫斯特镇为背景，由在曼彻斯特、奥尔德姆和柴郡拍摄的镜头组成。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/whats-on/netflix-fool-once-filmed-manchester-28331070" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《曼彻斯特晚报》</em></a>报道，许多场景是在曼彻斯特机场附近的环形跑道游客公园、卡斯尔菲尔德高架桥、亚历山德拉公园、斯托克波特的防空洞和布拉姆霍尔村拍摄的。</p><p>阿利庄园 (Arley Hall) 是柴郡的一座乡间别墅，在该剧中，朱迪丝 (乔安娜·拉姆利饰) 的家法姆伍德 (Farmwood) 也被使用。 Netflix 在 Instagram 上证实，BBC 剧集<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><em>《浴血黑帮</em></a>》中汤米·谢尔比 (Tommy Shelby) 的宏伟庄园也曾在同一地点出现。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1m27YxvfEB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.8